&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Access Holdings is a next-generation alternative asset manager providing investors with access to the lower-middle market. Founded in 2013, Access Holdings has approximately $2.3 billion in assets under management. The firm implements its systematic research and data-driven operating model - The Access Edge - to partner with lower-middle market businesses in industries essential to economic growth and resilience. For more information, please visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.accessholdings.com&quot;&gt;www.accessholdings.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;337&quot; data-end=&quot;469&quot;&gt;At Access Holdings, we build lasting partnerships and market-leading businesses—and we know great talent is at the center of it all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;471&quot; data-end=&quot;755&quot;&gt;By joining the &lt;strong data-start=&quot;486&quot; data-end=&quot;511&quot;&gt;Access Talent Network&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;re letting us know you&#39;re open to future opportunities with our firm or across our growing portfolio. Whether you&#39;re early in your career or a seasoned leader, we want to understand your interests, strengths, and where you&#39;d like to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;757&quot; data-end=&quot;977&quot;&gt;We&#39;re a collaborative, growth-focused team that values curiosity, ownership, and thoughtful problem-solving. If you’re excited by the idea of working hands-on to scale exceptional businesses, we’d love to stay connected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;979&quot; data-end=&quot;1039&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;979&quot; data-end=&quot;1039&quot;&gt;When you submit your information, here&#39;s what to expect:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1040&quot; data-end=&quot;1254&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1040&quot; data-end=&quot;1096&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1042&quot; data-end=&quot;1096&quot;&gt;We&#39;ll take note of your interests and experience areas&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1097&quot; data-end=&quot;1159&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1099&quot; data-end=&quot;1159&quot;&gt;If a relevant role opens up, our team may reach out directly&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1160&quot; data-end=&quot;1254&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1162&quot; data-end=&quot;1254&quot;&gt;Even if there’s no immediate match, we’ll keep your profile in mind for future opportunities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1256&quot; data-end=&quot;1416&quot;&gt;We welcome diverse backgrounds and perspectives and are always interested in connecting with people who are passionate about building businesses!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Access Holdings is a next-generation alternative asset manager providing investors with access to the lower-middle market. Founded in 2013, Access Holdings has approximately $2.3 billion in assets under management. The firm implements its systematic research and data-driven operating model - The Access Edge - to partner with lower-middle market businesses in industries essential to economic growth and resilience. For more information, please visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.accessholdings.com&quot;&gt;www.accessholdings.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;POSITION OVERVIEW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:320,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Access Holdings is building Access Holdings Capital Markets (AHCM), a new registered broker-dealer&amp;nbsp;anticipated&amp;nbsp;to receive FINRA approval in July 2026. AHCM will serve as a fully integrated capital markets platform supporting the firm&#39;s lower-middle market strategy,&amp;nbsp;including&amp;nbsp;M&amp;amp;A advisory and&amp;nbsp;capital raising,&amp;nbsp;while also expanding to serve third-party clients over time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:40,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Access Holdings is seeking a Principal for Access Holdings Capital Markets (AHCM),&amp;nbsp;an entrepreneurial, licensed securities professional (Series 24 and Series 79) who will partner with the Head of the Broker-Dealer to build and scale AHCM, while operating with the independence and authority to own initiatives, drive outcomes, and&amp;nbsp;lead the platform as it matures. This is a rare opportunity to help build an institutional-quality broker-dealer from the ground up within a well-capitalized, growth-stage alternative asset manager. The right candidate combines deep broker-dealer operational and compliance&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;with credit capital markets fluency, a commercial mindset, and the entrepreneurial drive to build something enduring. The&amp;nbsp;Principal&amp;nbsp;reports to&amp;nbsp;Chris Blackwell,&amp;nbsp;Partner&amp;nbsp;and Head of AHCM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:40,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;In addition to broker-dealer leadership responsibilities, the&amp;nbsp;Principal&amp;nbsp;will lead the Access Holdings Credit Capital Markets team,&amp;nbsp;organizing and leading all third-party financing efforts for new platform formation as well as portfolio company add-on financing initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:40,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:320,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Develop&amp;nbsp;the Broker-Dealer Platform&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:200,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:40}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
